This Coffee Ordering System should have the following:

Login page
Admin
Barista

Menu Section
Coffee Name
Offered Sizes (small, medium, large)
Offered Temperature (hot, cold)
Possible add ons along with the quantity and additional fees
Respective prices (for size, temperature)

(Only available on specific dates)
Special (Seasonal) Menu Section
Special Coffee Name
Offered Sizes (small, medium, large)
Offered Temperature (hot, cold)
Possible add ons along with the quantity and additional fees
Respective prices (for size, temperature)

Order Section
Customer Name (To call, pick-up)
Order Details (coffee name and its respective temperature and size (if applicable, its respective add ons)
Quantity per order
If applicable: quantity per add ons
Total of the order/s

Breakdown (Can be Reciept)
Name of the shop
Date and Time
Served By: (Employee Name)
__________________________
To be picked up by: (Customer Name)
Order Detail (Format)
Coffee Name (Temperature) - Size - Original Price x Quantity = Total
(if applicable) Add on name - Quantity - Additional Fee = FinalTotal
(To be repeated if there are many orders)
Grand total of the order
